[h3 
	" Who is 
	(__wikiLink|NesVideoAgent)
	"?
	$LF
]h3
[p 
	[img class=embedright src=http://bisqbot.stc.cx/bisqbot.jpg 
	]img
	$LF
	"NesVideoAgent was a humble drone of 
	[a class=extlink href=http://bisqbot.stc.cx/ rel=nofollow 
		"BisqBot
	]a
	",
	$LF
	"created in 2004-04-25. 
	[a href=/forum/p/405686#405686 
		"Here's the story
	]a
	" as Bisqwit tells it.
	$LF
]p
[h4 
	" NES video agent
	$LF
]h4
[p 
	"Its primary purpose was to sit on the 
	(__wikiLink|IRC Channel)
	$LF
	"and report on everything that happens on
	$LF
	"the 
	[a href=/forum/ 
		"discussion forums
	]a
	".
	$LF
]p
[p 
	"(Actually, these features are implemented in BisqBot, not NesVideoAgent. Explained below.)
	$LF
]p
[p 
	"It also told us when new submissions have been made or new movies
	$LF
	"have been published.
	$LF
]p
[p 
	"It had some unique abilities as well, such as 
	[a href=/forum/viewtopic.php?t=5968 
		"automatic screenshoting
	]a
	".
	$LF
]p
[h4 
	" TAS Video Agent
	$LF
]h4
[p 
	"On 2009-07-03 the bot in the IRC Channel was rewritten by 
	(__wikiLink|user:Nach)
	" in C using standard UNIX sockets and pipes for the new server, and renamed to 
	(__wikiLink|TAS Video Agent)
	".
	$LF
]p
[h4 
	" Scapegoat
	$LF
]h4
[p 
	"Now, the meaning of its life is to be the one to blame when
	$LF
	"something is done on the server-side, such as deleting 400
	$LF
	"accounts of the 
	(__wikiLink|Most Active Posters|forum users)
	".
	$LF
]p
[h4 
	" BisqBot agent
	$LF
]h4
[p 
	"Initially, as a tertiary function, it worked as a gateway, or 
	[em 
		"agent
	]em
	", to 
	[a class=extlink href=http://bisqbot.stc.cx/ rel=nofollow 
		"BisqBot
	]a
	".
	$LF
	"NesVideoAgent's "agent" feature made it possible for BisqBot's utilities
	$LF
	"to be used on 
	[tt 
		"#nesvideos
	]tt
	" despite BisqBot himself not being present:
	$LF
	"NesVideoAgent would relay both the queries and their responses.
	$LF
	"Sometimes the relaying would happen through Bisqwit's own client.
	$LF
	"NesVideoAgent himself did not possess any special functionality.
	$LF
]p
[p 
	"The utilities would be accessed with the 
	[tt 
		".
	]tt
	" commands such as the following:
	$LF
]p
[ul 
	[li 
		" Calculators:
		$LF
		[ul 
			[li 
				" 
				[tt 
					".cl
				]tt
				" ― Google-style calculator with units (implemented with GNU Units)
				$LF
			]li
			[li 
				" 
				[tt 
					".cm
				]tt
				" ― Maxima style math utility; does polynomial solving and a lot more
				$LF
			]li
			[li 
				" 
				[tt 
					".ce
				]tt
				" ― Obsolete engineering units calculator
				$LF
			]li
		]ul
		" 
		[tt 
			".google
		]tt
		" (Google search)
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
